Summary: Only saw object after downloading pics to computer
divs: sighting detailsthis event happened during the summer of 2006 while on vacation in cape cod. although the object is fuzzy, i believe it looks identical to the one submitted by the person working in afghanistan on 4\4\08, and because of that felt compelled to post my picture. as in other cases, i had no knowledge of the object until the pictures were downloaded to my computer. other shots taken immediately before and after did not contain the object. if you look closely, the object is just right of center in the sky. i am also attaching an enlarged view.
